{"prompt": "Create an inviting website for a craft brewery. The layout should feature a warm amber orange.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Brew Haven Craft Brewery</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f0e6d2;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #d48c46;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h1, h2 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            color: #ffffff;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1200x400/d48c46/ffffff?text=Brew+Haven+Craft+Brewery');\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            height: 400px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-left: 4px solid #d48c46;\n            background-color: #fdfaf6;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        .section h3 