em\">\n                    <h4>Amber Ale</h4>\n                    <p>A balanced classic with caramel malt sweetness and a hint of hop bitterness. Smooth and satisfying.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"beer-item\">\n                    <h4>Hoppy IPA</h4>\n                    <p>Bold hop aroma with citrus and pine notes, balanced by a robust malt backbone. For the hop lover.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"beer-item\">\n                    <h4>Stout Majesty</h4>\n                    <p>Rich, dark, and smooth with notes of roasted coffee and chocolate. A decadent treat.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"beer-item\">\n                    <h4>Pale Lager</h4>\n                    <p>Crisp, clean, and refreshing. Perfectly brewed for easy drinking and pure enjoyment.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Visit Us</h3>\n            <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Brewery Lane, Craftsville, CA 90210</p>\n            <p><strong>Hours:</strong></p>\n            <p>Monday - Thursday: 3 PM - 10 PM</p>\n            <p>Friday - Saturday: 12 PM - 11 PM</p>\n            <p>Sunday: 12 PM - 8 PM</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Brew Haven Craft Brewery. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}